{"data":{"featured":{"edges":[{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"CrossMeter (Winner @ ETH NYC 2025)","cover":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/png;base64,"},"images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/c3ce41e613fb4acc2020e80c0ff19c66/c2856/CrossMeter.png","srcSet":"/static/c3ce41e613fb4acc2020e80c0ff19c66/68202/CrossMeter.png 175w,\n/static/c3ce41e613fb4acc2020e80c0ff19c66/dea39/CrossMeter.png 350w,\n/static/c3ce41e613fb4acc2020e80c0ff19c66/c2856/CrossMeter.png 700w,\n/static/c3ce41e613fb4acc2020e80c0ff19c66/7caad/CrossMeter.png 1400w","sizes":"(min-width: 700px) 700px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/c3ce41e613fb4acc2020e80c0ff19c66/1934d/CrossMeter.avif 175w,\n/static/c3ce41e613fb4acc2020e80c0ff19c66/02566/CrossMeter.avif 350w,\n/static/c3ce41e613fb4acc2020e80c0ff19c66/e9420/CrossMeter.avif 700w,\n/static/c3ce41e613fb4acc2020e80c0ff19c66/e3408/CrossMeter.avif 1400w","type":"image/avif","sizes":"(min-width: 700px) 700px, 100vw"},{"srcSet":"/static/c3ce41e613fb4acc2020e80c0ff19c66/745fa/CrossMeter.webp 175w,\n/static/c3ce41e613fb4acc2020e80c0ff19c66/ec351/CrossMeter.webp 350w,\n/static/c3ce41e613fb4acc2020e80c0ff19c66/9c274/CrossMeter.webp 700w,\n/static/c3ce41e613fb4acc2020e80c0ff19c66/650e0/CrossMeter.webp 1400w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 700px) 700px, 100vw"}]},"width":700,"height":401}}},"tech":["Circle Swap","PayPal PYUSD","FastAPI","Mintlify","Solidity"],"github":"https://github.com/CrossMeter","external":"https://ethglobal.com/showcase/crossmeter-w9zay","cta":"temp"},"html":"<p>Single line billing infra for web3. CrossMeter uses stable-coin settlement rails enabling customers to reliably receive funds on preferred chain. With messy payment integrations out of the way, projects now become products. Users are no longer limited to a single chain, giving more exposure. Abstracting away hardest parts of crypto payments, we deliver a true “single-line billing infra” for stablecoin transactions. Inspired by <a href=\"https://useautumn.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">https://useautumn.com/</a>.</p>"}},{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"APIWink (Winner @ ETH SFO 2024)","cover":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/png;base64,"},"images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/e0ea271867180e3c4a1f6dadc76370ce/5b9fe/APIWink.png","srcSet":"/static/e0ea271867180e3c4a1f6dadc76370ce/aa78d/APIWink.png 175w,\n/static/e0ea271867180e3c4a1f6dadc76370ce/aa35b/APIWink.png 350w,\n/static/e0ea271867180e3c4a1f6dadc76370ce/5b9fe/APIWink.png 700w,\n/static/e0ea271867180e3c4a1f6dadc76370ce/bc8ac/APIWink.png 1400w","sizes":"(min-width: 700px) 700px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/e0ea271867180e3c4a1f6dadc76370ce/34a73/APIWink.avif 175w,\n/static/e0ea271867180e3c4a1f6dadc76370ce/09479/APIWink.avif 350w,\n/static/e0ea271867180e3c4a1f6dadc76370ce/6fd9f/APIWink.avif 700w,\n/static/e0ea271867180e3c4a1f6dadc76370ce/ffcd2/APIWink.avif 1400w","type":"image/avif","sizes":"(min-width: 700px) 700px, 100vw"},{"srcSet":"/static/e0ea271867180e3c4a1f6dadc76370ce/6b523/APIWink.webp 175w,\n/static/e0ea271867180e3c4a1f6dadc76370ce/28fc2/APIWink.webp 350w,\n/static/e0ea271867180e3c4a1f6dadc76370ce/12b97/APIWink.webp 700w,\n/static/e0ea271867180e3c4a1f6dadc76370ce/a2c7b/APIWink.webp 1400w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 700px) 700px, 100vw"}]},"width":700,"height":412}}},"tech":["Skale Network","Dynamic.xyz","Flask","Solidity","GitBook"],"github":"https://github.com/ApiWink","external":"https://ethglobal.com/showcase/apiwink-2ogub","cta":"temp"},"html":"<p>APIWink at core is an API micro-lending service, ideal to attract more users and reduce costs. Traditionally monthly/yearly API subscription models are costly for devs experimenting APIs for their platform. This micro-lending service enables purchasing \"API Count\" for Skale programmed currency. This pay per use model offers flexibility to user, exposure to provider while being revenue positive for them and APIWink platform.</p>"}},{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"QBaG (Finalist @ SIH 2022)","cover":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/png;base64,"},"images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/8a2b1448f3aab5344501a3383f00c6e6/bc3b9/QBaG.png","srcSet":"/static/8a2b1448f3aab5344501a3383f00c6e6/9a130/QBaG.png 175w,\n/static/8a2b1448f3aab5344501a3383f00c6e6/a3fa1/QBaG.png 350w,\n/static/8a2b1448f3aab5344501a3383f00c6e6/bc3b9/QBaG.png 700w","sizes":"(min-width: 700px) 700px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/8a2b1448f3aab5344501a3383f00c6e6/dae43/QBaG.avif 175w,\n/static/8a2b1448f3aab5344501a3383f00c6e6/d7667/QBaG.avif 350w,\n/static/8a2b1448f3aab5344501a3383f00c6e6/7ec1a/QBaG.avif 700w","type":"image/avif","sizes":"(min-width: 700px) 700px, 100vw"},{"srcSet":"/static/8a2b1448f3aab5344501a3383f00c6e6/5d873/QBaG.webp 175w,\n/static/8a2b1448f3aab5344501a3383f00c6e6/26a00/QBaG.webp 350w,\n/static/8a2b1448f3aab5344501a3383f00c6e6/f23f0/QBaG.webp 700w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 700px) 700px, 100vw"}]},"width":700,"height":394}}},"tech":["Django REST","Simple JWT","Tensorflow","React","Material UI"],"github":"https://github.com/Team-Executables/qbag-backend","external":"https://github.com/Team-Executables/qbag-backend","cta":"temp"},"html":"<p>Crowdsourcing model for board examinations developed at the finals of Smart India Hackathon '22. Developed an automated voting system for validation of questions, and functionality to generate question papers flexible with requirements. Integrated an SBERT model to reduce database redundancy for similar questions based on sentence semantics.</p>"}}]}}}